{"tid":872482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛情鳥飛走了 主人哭喚唔好走","createTime":"2018-10-22T17:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T23:08:43.000Z","uid":122068,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22451774e65b2c5ff173a4836efff8b3c65f5cf7","tid":872482,"uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T17:19:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TlvVUEJAGUE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTlvVUEJAGUE&d=nVIhS4%2BOkUQoKi76uSyciE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=54e1a12a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TlvVUEJAGUE</a><br />\n大角嘴發生走失鸚鵡事件，傍晚6時許，一名女主人帶同飼養的兩隻「愛情鳥」(又稱牡丹鸚鵡)大角嘴櫻桃街散步，其間她打開雀籠打算餵飼時，其中一隻鸚鵡「蕉蕉」突然飛出雀籠，並飛上附近一棵大樹上，女主人束手無策，報警求助。消防接報到場，升起雲梯協助，惟「蕉蕉」受驚反而飛走，不知所終，女主人不斷在旁哭喚「唔好走呀」，<span style=\"color: red;\"> 消防及警方只好收隊離場</span>。<br />\n<br />\n女主人表示，她飼養的一對「愛情鳥」約於年半前購買，<span style=\"color: red;\"> 每隻約500元，</span>今次走失的「蕉蕉」為雄性，過往未曾試過飛走。<br />\n<br />\n牡丹鸚鵡，又稱「愛情鳥」或「情侶鸚鵡」，牠們在鸚鵡中屬於小型鳥類，但是在愛情鳥中卻是屬於大型鳥類。因為牡丹鸚鵡體色鮮艷多變，而且繁殖能力很強，所以適合養鳥的初學者作為入門。據講，情侶鸚鵡因其深情的天性而得名情侶鸚鵡會與伴侶形影不離，相依相偎，而且多是會廝守終生。<br />\n<br />\n「愛情鳥」趁開籠逃脫 女主人哭喚︰唔好走呀<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181021&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58820137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181021%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58820137&d=nVIhS4%2BOkUQoKi76uSyciE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=aa845708\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181021%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58820137&h=ebd5ee4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181021&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58820137</a><br />\n<br />\n真係難為班消防員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要幫你捉雀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔係緊急服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係夠薑打999叫人幫你<img src=\"/